1
00:00:00,410 --> 00:00:02,140
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:02,140 --> 00:00:03,640
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,640 --> 00:00:05,040
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:11,120 --> 00:00:12,180
Hye Ra.

5
00:00:13,520 --> 00:00:15,120
You can rest now.

6
00:00:18,490 --> 00:00:20,090
Fall asleep here beside me.

7
00:00:22,330 --> 00:00:23,330
Forever.

8
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:34,340
Your voice...

9
00:00:36,510 --> 00:00:39,180
used to be so comforting and sweet.

10
00:00:41,710 --> 00:00:43,420
There was a time...

11
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:49,290
when just hearing your voice
made my heart skip a beat.

12
00:00:51,660 --> 00:00:52,960
I love you.

13
00:00:55,460 --> 00:00:56,660
I know.

14
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:02,470
I know how much you loved me.

15
00:01:07,110 --> 00:01:08,470
But now,

16
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:12,140
it's time your love ended.

17
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,980
That's right.
I'm telling you I did it.

18
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:53,320
I took care of
the mother of Jin Se Hoon,

19
00:01:53,420 --> 00:01:54,790
the former Vice Chairman of Kunhyang,

20
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:56,390
because Jin Tae Seok ordered me to.

21
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,890
Are you saying
you committed the murder yourself?

22
00:01:59,660 --> 00:02:02,660
Come on, Detective.
What century are you living in?

23
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:06,400
Do you really think people like us
get our hands dirty?

24
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:08,200
That's what money is for.

25
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:11,770
- What about Jin Tae Seok?
- He's already gone.

26
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:15,570
- What do you mean, "gone?"
- Are you deaf, Detective?

27
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,480
He's dead.

28
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,210
Then do you have a witness...

29
00:02:22,350 --> 00:02:25,220
to this murder-for-hire
you're confessing to?

30
00:02:25,350 --> 00:02:28,850
Why do I need a witness?
I'm right here confessing to you.

31
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:34,230
I was the one trading Kunhyang stock
using a borrowed-name account.

32
00:02:34,530 --> 00:02:35,760
It wasn't Joo Ha Neul.

33
00:02:36,130 --> 00:02:37,730
Why are you trying to take the fall
for him?

34
00:02:37,830 --> 00:02:40,670
"Take the fall?"
What are you talking about?

35
00:02:40,930 --> 00:02:43,470
Come on, I'm turning myself in,
so why won't you take my word for it?

36
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,240
Where did I put it? Hold on.

37
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,440
Here.

38
00:02:49,010 --> 00:02:51,010
Here's your evidence.
It's all in here.

39
00:02:51,010 --> 00:02:53,510
It says I'm the one who traded
the stocks under a borrowed name.

40
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:56,780
And that David Kay, that's my alias.

41
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,880
What else was there?

42
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,850
The Crown Capital.

43
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:03,890
The company went through
a massive tax audit a while ago.

44
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:07,130
Turns out I embezzled
a ton of money.

45
00:03:08,390 --> 00:03:09,930
Chairman Gong...

46
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:15,470
Don't cry on an empty stomach.
Eat up, then cry all you want.

47
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:20,840
She's the sweetest girl
in the world,

48
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:23,310
but I called her a wicked witch
and cursed her out.

49
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,210
For a son that isn't even her own,

50
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:27,680
and she cherishes
more than her own child,

51
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:31,680
she sacrificed herself,
for crying out loud.

52
00:03:47,070 --> 00:03:48,130
You've been through so much.

53
00:03:48,130 --> 00:03:49,470
I'm not guilty?
How is that possible?

54
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:51,370
Chairman Gong Nan Sook...

55
00:03:52,940 --> 00:03:53,970
turned herself in.

56
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,150
So, Jin Tae Seok
is really dead, right?

57
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,620
I still can't believe it.

58
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:08,320
You just came from his funeral.
Why is it so hard to believe?

59
00:04:08,550 --> 00:04:09,950
He's like an immortal, isn't he?

60
00:04:10,390 --> 00:04:12,120
I'm worried
he might rise from his own grave.

61
00:04:12,390 --> 00:04:13,520
That's not going to happen.

62
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:17,060
He took my child's life...

63
00:04:17,730 --> 00:04:19,560
and killed Ki Beom.

64
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:21,800
I can finally put him
out of my mind.

65
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:25,040
You've suffered so much,

66
00:04:25,970 --> 00:04:27,470
enduring everything to get here.

67
00:04:29,110 --> 00:04:30,270
You have too, Manager Hwang.

68
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:34,580
I don't know why,
but I'm dying for a drink today.

69
00:04:35,350 --> 00:04:38,720
I'd kill for just one shot
of something strong.

70
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:42,390
I was hoping we could go elsewhere,
not here.

71
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:45,390
Would you care to join me?

72
00:04:59,370 --> 00:05:02,410
Rest in peace, my sweet baby.

73
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:06,310
Mommy will come visit sometimes...

74
00:05:08,650 --> 00:05:11,480
with him.

75
00:05:28,330 --> 00:05:29,500
Ki Beom,

76
00:05:30,570 --> 00:05:31,670
you're smiling now, aren't you?

77
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:32,800
(Cha Ki Beom, Born: April 7, 1966,
Date of Death: November 28, 2025)

78
00:05:33,170 --> 00:05:35,070
That's right. Go on and smile.

79
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,610
Your name has been cleared,

80
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:40,310
and Jin Tae Seok has fallen
into the abyss.

81
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:43,410
He got his just deserts.

82
00:05:44,850 --> 00:05:48,150
Now you can finally
relax and have a drink.

83
00:06:08,670 --> 00:06:10,680
(Kunhyang Group)

84
00:06:13,810 --> 00:06:17,080
Do you really have to step down
as chairman like this?

85
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:20,720
It wasn't my place to begin with.

86
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:23,290
I've done what I came to do,

87
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,220
so now it's time
for me to step down.

88
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:28,690
I feel the same way as Ha Neul.

89
00:06:29,930 --> 00:06:32,660
I'm leaving Kunhyang, too.

90
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:36,700
I've been thinking
about this for a long time.

91
00:06:37,940 --> 00:06:39,700
All of this misfortune started...

92
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:41,740
when I became
the matriarch of Kunhyang,

93
00:06:41,810 --> 00:06:44,940
and from my ambition
to reach the very top.

94
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:49,650
I'm going to entrust Kunhyang
to a professional CEO,

95
00:06:50,820 --> 00:06:52,050
and I'll be leaving as well,

96
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:53,890
with you, Jung Won.

97
00:07:07,670 --> 00:07:08,670
Oh my...

98
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,810
Good grief.

99
00:07:17,980 --> 00:07:20,710
Why did you come all this way?
There's nothing good to see here.

100
00:07:21,110 --> 00:07:24,980
I heard you decorated
your cell like a hotel room.

101
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:29,550
Are you staying warm enough?

102
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:31,760
I'm fine right now.

103
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:34,490
Manager Gu brings me warm things
from time to time.

104
00:07:36,330 --> 00:07:37,460
I figured as much.

105
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:45,000
So? Did you have something to say?

106
00:07:49,470 --> 00:07:53,010
I won't be able to visit you
for a while.

107
00:07:57,980 --> 00:08:00,180
I guess you're going somewhere.

108
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:02,990
I've already booked the flights.

109
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:06,020
How many tickets did you get? Two?

110
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:09,530
Or did you get four tickets
for a round trip?

111
00:08:13,660 --> 00:08:16,030
Make sure you go
with the one you love.

112
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:19,800
And make sure
you come back together.

113
00:08:27,910 --> 00:08:29,650
Please stay healthy, Mother.

114
00:08:38,620 --> 00:08:39,860
Hearing you call me "Mother"...

115
00:08:41,590 --> 00:08:43,260
sounds so nice.

116
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:45,160
It does.

117
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:53,800
You know, out of all the times
I've seen you,

118
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,840
you've never looked...

119
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,010
more at peace than this.

120
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,880
I do, don't I?

121
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:09,050
Go on.

122
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:30,240
Congratulations,
Chief Director Jin Se Mi.

123
00:09:31,010 --> 00:09:32,010
My congratulations as well.

124
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:34,780
I've been appointed to a position
of great responsibility.

125
00:09:35,050 --> 00:09:37,950
I'll be counting on all of your help
moving forward.

126
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,750
- I'm counting on you.
- You don't even have to ask.

127
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,590
By the way,
what about Joo Young Chae?

128
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:46,020
Right. I haven't seen
her face around lately.

129
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:49,330
Joo Young Chae
has submitted her resignation.

130
00:09:49,690 --> 00:09:51,860
And the company has accepted it.

131
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:02,770
So Chairman Gong Nan Sook
took the fall for Joo Ha Neul?

132
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:06,480
He has all the luck.

133
00:10:08,010 --> 00:10:11,050
How are you feeling?
Are you starting to show yet?

134
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:15,190
Do you really have to wear
something that tight? Goodness.

135
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,490
I never imagined...

136
00:10:18,590 --> 00:10:20,490
you'd end up in prison.

137
00:10:21,290 --> 00:10:22,590
I actually like it.

138
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:26,130
If I'd known,
I would've turned myself in sooner.

139
00:10:32,970 --> 00:10:35,840
How are things with Jin Se Hoon?

140
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:38,480
Se Hoon will be the chairman
of Kunhyang Group again soon.

141
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,910
And I'm going to make that happen.

142
00:10:41,710 --> 00:10:43,810
Are you still driven
by that same greed?

143
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:45,550
How is that greed?

144
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:48,390
I'm just trying to take
what's rightfully ours.

145
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:53,520
Young Chae.

146
00:10:56,290 --> 00:10:57,630
Just live a good life.

147
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:00,200
Don't you worry about me.

148
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:04,270
- I'll live well and be just fine.
- Please.

149
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,640
Just live a good life, okay?

150
00:11:08,170 --> 00:11:09,470
Of course I will.

151
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:15,780
I'm finally done being your puppet,
and I've even found true love.

152
00:11:18,780 --> 00:11:20,520
You just worry about yourself, Mom.

153
00:11:21,250 --> 00:11:24,560
And don't get into fights
while you're in prison.

154
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:33,760
What's wrong?

155
00:11:35,530 --> 00:11:37,000
It's all my fault.

156
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:40,600
No matter how much my mom doted
on Ha Neul,

157
00:11:41,370 --> 00:11:43,370
I never thought she'd go so far
as to turn herself in.

158
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:46,110
I never thought...

159
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:49,610
she was the type
to sacrifice herself for family.

160
00:11:49,980 --> 00:11:51,880
I guess I was wrong about her.

161
00:11:52,650 --> 00:11:55,620
You'll startle A Reum. Calm down.

162
00:11:57,490 --> 00:12:00,260
This is what comes around.

163
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:03,130
What about us?

164
00:12:03,430 --> 00:12:04,630
What do you mean, "us?"

165
00:12:04,930 --> 00:12:06,800
We've done our share of bad things,
you know.

166
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:09,170
- What?
- The karma.

167
00:12:10,770 --> 00:12:12,170
You don't think that applies to us?

168
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:16,010
What more could possibly happen
to us?

169
00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:17,740
We're the victims here.

170
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:19,280
Maybe...

171
00:12:19,810 --> 00:12:22,110
- we've already faced our karma.
- Young Chae.

172
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:24,650
My goal was to become the lady
of the Kunhyang Group.

173
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,120
And yet...

174
00:12:28,450 --> 00:12:31,060
to think I'd end up falling for you
when you have nothing...

175
00:12:32,420 --> 00:12:34,060
I guess
this really is my punishment.

176
00:12:49,610 --> 00:12:50,770
Hye Ra.

177
00:12:53,580 --> 00:12:55,510
I'm glad you could make it,
old friend!

178
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:58,950
What's with the "old friend" act?

179
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:01,320
You never change, do you,
Gong Nan Sook?

180
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:04,290
You look like you're on vacation.
Your skin's so clear.

181
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:08,230
I'm in my element, aren't I?
I'm a total rock star in here.

182
00:13:08,730 --> 00:13:12,760
I guess I was made for the slammer.
I could stay here forever.

183
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:14,870
What?

184
00:13:16,330 --> 00:13:18,770
You didn't forget what I asked,
did you?

185
00:13:19,470 --> 00:13:20,570
Han Hye Ra.

186
00:13:21,070 --> 00:13:22,270
Come on, darling.

187
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:24,410
You'll help me, right?

188
00:13:25,410 --> 00:13:26,610
How?

189
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,810
I have two favors to ask.

190
00:13:31,350 --> 00:13:32,720
My two good boys.

191
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:35,590
Make sure they're set up
for a good life.

192
00:13:35,990 --> 00:13:37,820
I'm guessing one is Joo Ha Neul.

193
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,460
And the other one?

194
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:41,760
My dear Yeong Soo,
who looks like a cartoon character.

195
00:13:42,590 --> 00:13:43,690
Manager Gu?

196
00:13:43,990 --> 00:13:47,870
- Yes.
- How do I give them a good life?

197
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:49,770
And the second favor?

198
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:51,540
It's about my Young Chae.

199
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:55,870
She's my daughter,
and I'm the one who ruined her.

200
00:13:56,610 --> 00:13:59,340
Turns out she's genuinely in love
with Jin Se Hoon.

201
00:14:00,380 --> 00:14:03,210
- I know.
- Don't pretend you don't.

202
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:05,150
So, please look after them.

203
00:14:06,420 --> 00:14:08,120
What do you want me to do?

204
00:14:09,590 --> 00:14:11,060
Kick them out of Kunhyang.

205
00:14:13,420 --> 00:14:15,790
That's "looking after them?"
That's kicking them to the curb.

206
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:18,130
It's the only way for Young Chae
and Jin Se Hoon...

207
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,700
to finally live a normal life.

208
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:25,270
(Chairman Gu Yeong Soo)

209
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:32,310
Thank you.

210
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:34,310
Chairman Gong Nan Sook.

211
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:46,820
I'm Director Yoon Min Jung,
and I'll be helping you from today.

212
00:14:48,490 --> 00:14:49,490
This is kind of awkward.

213
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,830
There's no need for formalities,
Director Yoon.

214
00:14:52,330 --> 00:14:55,130
Sir, here is your briefing material
for today.

215
00:14:58,100 --> 00:15:00,670
Even if I were a genius,
how could I possibly read all this?

216
00:15:00,740 --> 00:15:04,310
You're succeeding Chairman Gong
as head of The Crown Capital.

217
00:15:04,380 --> 00:15:07,850
Former Advisor Han Hye Ra
also gave me specific instructions.

218
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:11,350
- Which were?
- "Make a real chairman out of him."

219
00:15:11,650 --> 00:15:13,920
"Min Jung,
I'm holding you responsible."

220
00:15:14,990 --> 00:15:18,720
So you're not my secretary,
but more like my warden?

221
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:19,960
That's correct, sir.

222
00:15:27,530 --> 00:15:30,400
So Gu Yeong Soo is the new chairman
of Crown Capital?

223
00:15:31,100 --> 00:15:32,470
He'll do a great job.

224
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:35,240
He may act like a fool,
but he's a real genius.

225
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:37,010
And as for Young Chae and Se Hoon,

226
00:15:37,410 --> 00:15:39,240
I did exactly as you asked.

227
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:43,710
Good.

228
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:47,990
See? I told you we have
some serious chemistry.

229
00:15:48,190 --> 00:15:49,650
And you're not worried
about me at all?

230
00:15:49,990 --> 00:15:51,960
Why would I worry about you?

231
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:55,930
By the way,

232
00:15:56,330 --> 00:15:58,200
are you really going
to give it all up?

233
00:16:00,730 --> 00:16:02,470
I have to atone...

234
00:16:03,230 --> 00:16:05,100
for the sins I've committed.

235
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:10,640
I've got to hand it to you.

236
00:16:11,010 --> 00:16:13,680
- You're a tougher woman than I am.
- No.

237
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:15,880
Gong Nan Sook,
you're the better one.

238
00:16:16,250 --> 00:16:18,480
No, you've definitely got me beat.

239
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:22,820
But I'm the prettier one.
Let's get that straight, okay?

240
00:16:22,990 --> 00:16:26,760
Fine. You're the great, pretty one,
Gong Nan Sook. You win.

241
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,560
Good grief.

242
00:16:38,800 --> 00:16:40,670
I want you to come with me.

243
00:16:42,310 --> 00:16:44,040
(Incheon to Paris)

244
00:16:44,110 --> 00:16:47,180
The flight's in a week.
I'm heading to Paris for now.

245
00:16:48,810 --> 00:16:50,780
I've given up everything I had.

246
00:16:51,780 --> 00:16:53,550
So I'm sorry to ask you...

247
00:16:53,550 --> 00:16:55,320
to come with me
when I have nothing left.

248
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:00,760
Now that we can let go
of all our heavy burdens,

249
00:17:01,490 --> 00:17:02,860
I want us to live a simple,

250
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:04,800
happy life.

251
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:08,770
I want to share that kind of life
with you.

252
00:17:15,170 --> 00:17:17,070
We can take walks together.

253
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:20,210
We don't have to eat fancy food.

254
00:17:20,410 --> 00:17:22,950
Just being able to eat with you...

255
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:24,850
is enough for me.

256
00:17:25,620 --> 00:17:28,990
I want to live a life of happiness,

257
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:33,260
even if it's just full of smiles,

258
00:17:34,590 --> 00:17:36,190
with you, Jung Won.

259
00:17:36,930 --> 00:17:40,430
Just imagining it
makes my heart flutter.

260
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:41,930
And it fills me with so much joy.

261
00:17:51,610 --> 00:17:54,750
You more than deserve
that simple happiness.

262
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:58,180
Come with me.

263
00:18:11,700 --> 00:18:14,830
Mom, what do you want to do now?

264
00:18:15,630 --> 00:18:19,740
I'll just go with the flow
and let nature take its course.

265
00:18:25,140 --> 00:18:26,840
You're leaving...

266
00:18:28,350 --> 00:18:29,780
with Former Chairman Joo Ha Neul, right?

267
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:43,060
He's a good man.

268
00:18:45,060 --> 00:18:47,430
He truly cherishes...

269
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,570
and loves you.

270
00:18:59,110 --> 00:19:01,150
Why must you leave the Kunhyang house?

271
00:19:01,350 --> 00:19:02,510
Where will we live?

272
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:03,910
Anywhere we go...

273
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:05,950
will be more comfortable
than the Kunhyang house.

274
00:19:06,320 --> 00:19:09,150
Then let's go to my mom's house.
It's empty right now.

275
00:19:09,250 --> 00:19:11,090
And you need to make up
with Ha Neul already.

276
00:19:11,890 --> 00:19:13,920
Se Hoon, you're acting...

277
00:19:14,260 --> 00:19:16,060
so petty and small-minded
toward Ha Neul.

278
00:19:16,730 --> 00:19:18,460
What? "Petty?"

279
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:20,930
Is Ha Neul's success a crime?

280
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:24,270
He even resigned as chairman
and will move abroad.

281
00:19:24,330 --> 00:19:26,040
I can't face Joo Ha Neul.

282
00:19:26,040 --> 00:19:28,240
No, I'm never seeing him again.

283
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:38,250
(Joo Ha Neul)

284
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:54,770
Why would you call to have a drink
when there is nothing left to say?

285
00:19:58,070 --> 00:20:00,140
You must've wanted
an apology from me.

286
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:04,680
It's such a simple thing,

287
00:20:06,210 --> 00:20:08,050
but I never even managed
to apologize to you.

288
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:11,480
I'm sorry.

289
00:20:14,990 --> 00:20:16,550
Young Chae said...

290
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:19,420
that I was just jealous of you.

291
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:23,660
She was right. I admit it.

292
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:26,760
I was being petty.

293
00:20:27,630 --> 00:20:28,630
I'm glad...

294
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:33,970
that before I leave,
I got to talk to you one last time.

295
00:20:37,140 --> 00:20:38,180
Here.

296
00:20:49,420 --> 00:20:50,420
What do you want?

297
00:20:51,490 --> 00:20:53,960
Are you here to brag about
leaving with Ha Neul?

298
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:07,300
You and I...

299
00:21:08,940 --> 00:21:10,510
were always very different,

300
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:14,780
and we hated each other for it.

301
00:21:14,850 --> 00:21:17,010
"I was wrong,
but you were wrong, too,"

302
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,820
"so let's just call it even?"

303
00:21:20,350 --> 00:21:21,650
I can't stand that kind of talk.

304
00:21:22,220 --> 00:21:23,450
Me neither.

305
00:21:24,090 --> 00:21:25,090
I just...

306
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:27,620
wanted to sit down with you,
just the two of us,

307
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,330
and have a cup of tea like this.

308
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,030
I've decided...

309
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:35,930
to go back to studying design.

310
00:21:37,970 --> 00:21:40,840
That way, I won't be tempted
to steal your designs again.

311
00:21:42,210 --> 00:21:43,540
That's a great decision.

312
00:21:44,910 --> 00:21:45,910
And...

313
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:48,650
you won't be seeing me for a while.

314
00:21:49,610 --> 00:21:52,620
So, it must be true
that you're leaving with Ha Neul.

315
00:21:55,490 --> 00:21:56,950
What a relief.

316
00:21:57,890 --> 00:21:59,820
Just the thought of not having
to see your face...

317
00:21:59,820 --> 00:22:01,890
feels like a ten-year weight
has finally been lifted.

318
00:22:08,230 --> 00:22:09,270
I...

319
00:22:09,700 --> 00:22:11,940
still don't understand
Joo Young Chae.

320
00:22:12,870 --> 00:22:17,040
No, I can't understand her,
and I certainly can't forgive her.

321
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,640
But...

322
00:22:22,410 --> 00:22:26,150
now I have the emotional space...

323
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:28,650
to look into her troubled heart.

324
00:22:30,290 --> 00:22:32,020
Young Chae must have
been hurting too,

325
00:22:32,490 --> 00:22:33,790
just like I was.

326
00:22:35,830 --> 00:22:38,300
By seeing each other
at our most vulnerable...

327
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:40,860
and finding compassion
within ourselves,

328
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:42,970
the story
between Young Chae and me...

329
00:22:43,700 --> 00:22:45,870
can finally come to a pause.

330
00:23:13,430 --> 00:23:14,870
With Ha Neul?

331
00:23:19,470 --> 00:23:21,300
Do I even deserve that?

332
00:23:32,220 --> 00:23:34,080
I'm so sorry to you too.

333
00:23:34,080 --> 00:23:36,050
I have become
the daughter of your enemy.

334
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:40,020
I can't hate you for
what our parents did.

335
00:23:42,060 --> 00:23:44,230
As if nothing ever happened,

336
00:23:45,300 --> 00:23:46,930
am I allowed to be happy?

337
00:24:33,840 --> 00:24:36,780
Have a safe trip, Jung Won.

338
00:24:37,050 --> 00:24:38,480
You take care too, Se Mi,

339
00:24:39,050 --> 00:24:40,420
until we see each other again.

340
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:45,620
Call me as soon as you land.

341
00:24:48,390 --> 00:24:50,690
I love you, Mom.

342
00:24:56,730 --> 00:24:58,340
Just how pretty is she
trying to look?

343
00:24:59,140 --> 00:25:00,200
Honestly...

344
00:25:09,750 --> 00:25:11,410
Jung Won will be here any minute.

345
00:25:42,110 --> 00:25:44,050
But it's almost time to board.

346
00:25:47,220 --> 00:25:48,220
Jung Won.

347
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:52,320
I'm sorry, Ha Neul.

348
00:25:53,890 --> 00:25:55,160
Don't wait for me.

349
00:25:56,560 --> 00:25:57,560
Jung Won.

350
00:25:58,600 --> 00:26:01,130
More than anything,
I wanted to go with you.

351
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,700
Then let's just go together.

352
00:26:03,430 --> 00:26:04,570
But...

353
00:26:07,300 --> 00:26:08,540
I don't think I can.

354
00:26:11,170 --> 00:26:12,680
Why? What's wrong?

355
00:26:13,140 --> 00:26:14,540
Love isn't just about...

356
00:26:15,410 --> 00:26:17,250
being together.

357
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:21,450
How can you end things
between us like this? No, Jung Won

358
00:26:21,450 --> 00:26:22,490
Let's...

359
00:26:23,020 --> 00:26:24,520
just put things on hold for now.

360
00:26:26,190 --> 00:26:27,190
I...

361
00:26:29,190 --> 00:26:31,330
don't deserve to be happy yet.

362
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:36,470
To me,

363
00:26:37,370 --> 00:26:39,140
you'll always be my protector.

364
00:26:39,700 --> 00:26:41,140
You're my great, sheltering tree,

365
00:26:42,310 --> 00:26:43,470
my endless sky,

366
00:26:45,710 --> 00:26:46,710
and the roof over my head.

367
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:51,310
- Jung Won...
- If we're meant to be,

368
00:26:52,250 --> 00:26:53,620
we'll meet again.

369
00:26:56,690 --> 00:26:58,220
And when that time comes,

370
00:27:00,090 --> 00:27:01,560
you and I can start fresh.

371
00:27:11,700 --> 00:27:14,200
I love you, Jung Won.

372
00:27:16,140 --> 00:27:17,140
I...

373
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:20,580
love you too.

374
00:28:24,210 --> 00:28:29,580
(2 Years Later)

375
00:28:29,580 --> 00:28:30,680
(Somang Childcare Center)

376
00:28:43,090 --> 00:28:45,700
- Hey! Stop it!
- Hey, I want some too!

377
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:47,130
- Give it to me.
- No!

378
00:28:47,130 --> 00:28:50,500
- Kids, be careful. You'll get hurt.
- All right!

379
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:53,700
- Toss that one back!
- Hey, what about me?

380
00:28:53,770 --> 00:28:56,170
- Hey!
- Careful, you'll fall!

381
00:28:56,240 --> 00:28:57,840
- Hey, over here!
- Hey, give it to me!

382
00:28:58,640 --> 00:29:00,710
Lunchtime!

383
00:29:19,260 --> 00:29:22,870
Do you see that over there?
That's Kunhyang Group,

384
00:29:23,270 --> 00:29:26,340
and one day, it'll all be yours.

385
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:28,810
Now you know
why we named you Kun Hyang.

386
00:29:52,600 --> 00:29:53,600
You got another one.

387
00:29:58,640 --> 00:30:00,540
(To Jung Won: Hope you're well)

388
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:03,240
This time,
it's from London, England.

389
00:30:07,780 --> 00:30:09,710
It says his travel columns
were published as a book.

390
00:30:11,180 --> 00:30:12,620
I'd love to read that.

391
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:14,450
I'll have to check the bookstore.

392
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:55,360
By any chance,

393
00:30:57,430 --> 00:30:58,430
are you looking for this?

394
00:31:03,970 --> 00:31:07,200
("The Me I Met on My Travels")

395
00:31:10,470 --> 00:31:11,470
Ha Neul?

396
00:31:14,740 --> 00:31:15,810
How have you been?

397
00:31:24,090 --> 00:31:25,320
Well... Listen.

398
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:28,590
I'm pretty hungry.

399
00:31:31,360 --> 00:31:32,730
If you haven't eaten lunch,

400
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:34,630
do you want
to get some spicy rice cakes?

401
00:32:12,670 --> 00:32:18,170
(A Graceful Liar)

402
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:18,130
(Thank you for your love and support
for "A Graceful Liar.")

403
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,410
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
